{"tid":1856932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【請廣傳】醫護罷工，責任在於政府","createTime":"2020-02-02T02:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T05:46:53.000Z","uid":37528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8091981003741ee50005300372f366be8f61a33","tid":1856932,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"可預見聽日政府一定會將波射過去俾前線醫護，然後又話醫護唔為病人著想又盛<br />\n之後就有班藍屍配合幫手鬧醫護<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要緊記：醫護罷工責任在於政府<br />\n醫護唔罷工俾壓力政府，只會令所病毒人黎曬香港，到時就唔會有足夠資源香港真正需要醫療既人<br />\n<br />\nCase 1<br />\n唔罷工&gt;唔封關&gt;香港感染人數上升+大量病毒人黎香港搶醫療資源&gt;香港醫療制度collapse<br />\n<br />\nCase 2<br />\n罷工&gt;封關&gt;禁止病毒人入境&gt;香港人絕少部分人感染&gt;大部分香港人健康&gt;到時仆街政府課金俾支那又好點都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至少確保到香港人安全<br />\n<br />\nCase 3<br />\n罷工&gt;政府拒絕封關&gt;香港感染人數上升+大量病毒人黎香港搶醫療資源&gt;香港醫療制度collapse<br />\n<br />\n再者，<br />\n香港唔封關，世界封香港<br />\n醫護唔單止救緊香港人，仲間接救緊香港商界。而家根本所有國家都當曬香港係疫區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">醫護罷工係救緊香港人救緊香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有，政府同醫管局大把管理層都係醫生，點解醫護罷工，你地唔推上前線？你地有無人性？政府同醫管局管理層立即上前線，唔好剩係得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b145b352d31d97793039cba5c75f9ef042f988","tid":1856932,"uid":321803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"推 and retweet"},{"pid":"69430cacd27b5f3840fc7f310d2806168b63aaba","tid":1856932,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"政府唔止推醫護去死，仲係推全香港人去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由一開始班高官唔戴口罩，再到近期個個戴罩，再到近近期隻死肥豬疑似運口罩去自己屋企<br />\n擺明就係將大話蓋大話，直到最後無得隱瞞，就講：現階段唔係追究既時候<br />\n<br />\n唔可以俾班狗官得逞"},{"pid":"4bd8599fce7cace34998742cb253849bc5751faf","tid":1856932,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q8ouQZ9ecH8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq8ouQZ9ecH8&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=be893c5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q8ouQZ9ecH8</a>"},{"pid":"d32fba0c6caa44f2d7c9f456e47f9d696c73bb90","tid":1856932,"uid":55854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75e40cc6895f3ed1d6bc7977967990366caf1fa3","tid":1856932,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭不會出席談判會議，所以會議將會取消<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭星期日缺席談判 引致醫護罷工"},{"pid":"aad8db96e2d349cdf26ce17e20d3e9679dbf2c04","tid":1856932,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c384804efc349448e1c1d5754f9a01e2b1ce2571","tid":1856932,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"twitter都要多D人講解, 見唔多tweet 解釋罷工"}]}